# Frontend Environment Configuration

## Overview
This document provides comprehensive guidance for setting up the Spandan frontend environment configuration. It includes detailed instructions for development, testing, and deployment.

## Quick Start

### Development Environment
```bash
# 1. Create .env file in frontend directory
cd frontend
cat > .env.local << EOF
VITE_BASE_PATH=/spandan
VITE_SOCKET_URL=http://localhost:3001
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5002/api
EOF

# 2. Start the application
npm run dev
```

### Production Environment
```bash
# 1. Set environment variables
export VITE_BASE_PATH=/spandan
export VITE_SOCKET_URL=https://spandan.fun
export VITE_API_URL=https://spandan.fun/api

# 2. Build for production
npm run build

# 3. Deploy to your preferred hosting platform
```

## Configuration Files Structure

### Frontend Configuration
- **`frontend/.env.example`** - Complete configuration template
- **`frontend/.env.local`** - Local development overrides
- **`frontend/src/config.js`** - Runtime configuration
- **`frontend/.env.production`** - Production settings

### Configuration Files
- **`frontend/src/config.js`** - Central configuration
- **`.env.local`** - Local development settings
- **`.env.production`** - Production settings
- **`.env.test`** - Test configuration

## Configuration Template: frontend/.env.example

```env
# ==============================================================================
# Spandan Frontend Environment Configuration
# ==============================================================================
# Copy this file to .env.local and customize for your environment
# ==============================================================================

# Application Configuration
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VITE_BASE_PATH=/spandan            # Base path for the application
VITE_SOCKET_URL=http://localhost:3001  # WebSocket server URL
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5002/api # API base URL (optional)

# Frontend Environment
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VITE_API_BASE_URL=/api              # API base path
VITE_WS_PATH=/spandan/socket.io    # WebSocket path
VITE_MODE=development             # Application mode (development, production, test)

# API Configuration
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VITE_API_TIMEOUT=30000            # Request timeout in milliseconds
VITE_API_RETRY_COUNT=3            # Number of request retries
VITE_API_RETRY_DELAY=1000         # Delay between retries in milliseconds

# UI/UX Configuration
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VITE_THEME=auto                  # Theme: light, dark, or auto
VITE_DEFAULT_LANGUAGE=en        # Default language
VITE_ENABLE_SOUNDS=true          # Enable sound notifications
VITE_KEYBOARD_SHORTCUTS=true     # Enable keyboard shortcuts
VITE_LEADERBOARD_ANONYMOUS=false  # Show student names in leaderboard

# Feature Flags
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VITE_ENABLE_AI_GENERATION=true    # Enable AI question generation
VITE_ENABLE_TRANSCRIPTION=true    # Enable audio transcription
VITE_ENABLE_SSO=true            # Enable Samagama SSO
VITE_ENABLE_ANALYTICS=false       # Enable analytics tracking

# Security Configuration
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VITE_ENABLE_CORS=true            # Enable CORS
VITE_CORS_ORIGINS=https://spandan.fun,https://*.spandan.fun
VITE_ENABLE_CONTENT_SECURITY_POLICY=true
VITE_CONTENT_SECURITY_POLICY=default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline';

# Performance Configuration
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VITE_ENABLE_CODE_SPLITTING=true   # Enable code splitting
VITE_ENABLE_COMPRESSION=true      # Enable gzip compression
VITE_ENABLE_CACHE=true            # Enable caching
VITE_CACHE_DURATION=3600         # Cache duration in seconds

# Logging Configuration
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VITE_ENABLE_DEBUG_LOGS=false      # Enable debug logging
VITE_LOG_LEVEL=info              # Log level: debug, info, warn, error
VITE_LOG_MAX_SIZE=10485760        # Maximum log file size in bytes (10MB)
VITE_LOG_BACKUP_COUNT=5          # Number of log backup files

# Monitoring & Analytics
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VITE_TRACKING_ID=your-tracking-id  # Analytics tracking ID
VITE_ENABLE_PERFORMANCE_MONITORING=true  # Enable performance monitoring
VITE_ENABLE_ERROR_TRACKING=true   # Enable error tracking
VITE_ERROR_REPORTING_ENDPOINT=/api/errors  # Error reporting API endpoint

# Personalization
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VITE_THEME_PREFERENCE=local      # Theme preference: light, dark, or auto
VITE_TIMEZONE=America/New_York    # Timezone for date formatting
VITE_DATE_FORMAT=yyyy-MM-dd     # Date format
VITE_TIME_FORMAT=HH:mm          # Time format
VITE_NUMBER_FORMAT=#,##0.00     # Number format (en-US)

# Integration Configuration
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VITE_SAMAGAMA_URL=https://samagama.in  # Samagama SSO URL
VITE_SAMAGAMA_CLIENT_ID=your-client-id    # Samagama client ID
VITE_SAMAGAMA_SCOPE=user.read,user.write

# AI Model Configuration
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VITE_AI_MODEL_MINIMAX=chat-minimal
VITE_AI_MODEL_OPENAI=gpt-3.5-turbo
VITE_AI_MODEL_ANTHROPIC=claude-2
VITE_AI_MODEL_GOOGLE=gemini-pro

# AI Service Configuration
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VITE_AI_MAX_TOKENS=1000           # Maximum tokens per request
VITE_AI_TEMPERATURE=0.7          # AI model temperature
VITE_AI_TOP_P=0.9                 # AI top P parameter
VITE_AI_TIMEOUT=30000            # AI request timeout in milliseconds

# Audio/Video Configuration
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VITE_AUDIO_INPUT_DEVICE=default    # Default audio input device
VITE_AUDIO_SAMPLE_RATE=44100      # Audio sample rate
VITE_VIDEO_INPUT_DEVICE=null      # Video input device (for screen sharing)
VITE_VIDEO_RESOLUTION=1920x1080   # Video resolution

# Accessibility Configuration
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VITE_ENABLE_SCREEN_READER_SUPPORT=true  # Enable screen reader support
VITE_ENABLE_HIGH_CONTRAST_MODE=false   # Enable high contrast mode
VITE_ENABLE_FONT_SCALING=true          # Enable font scaling
VITE_ENABLE_ANIMATION_REDUCTION=false  # Reduce animations for accessibility

# ==============================================================================
# Production Environment Considerations
# ==============================================================================
# In production, consider these settings:

# 1. Secure API URLs
# VITE_SOCKET_URL=https://spandan.fun
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://spandan.fun/api
# VITE_SAMAGAMA_URL=https://samagama.in

# 2. Security settings
# VITE_ENABLE_CONTENT_SECURITY_POLICY=true
# VITE_ENABLE_DEBUG_LOGS=false
# VITE_LOG_LEVEL=warn

# 3. Performance optimization
# VITE_ENABLE_COMPRESSION=true
# VITE_ENABLE_CACHE=true
# VITE_ENABLE_CODE_SPLITTING=true

# 4. Analytics and monitoring
# VITE_ENABLE_ANALYTICS=true
# VITE_ENABLE_PERFORMANCE_MONITORING=true
# VITE_ENABLE_ERROR_TRACKING=true
# VITE_TRACKING_ID=your-production-tracking-id

# ==============================================================================
# Development Environment Overrides
# ==============================================================================
# Override any settings in .env.local for local development
# Example: set development-specific values
# VITE_MODE=development
# VITE_SOCKET_URL=http://localhost:3001
# VITE_ENABLE_DEBUG_LOGS=true
# VITE_LOG_LEVEL=debug
# VITE_ENABLE_ANALYTICS=false
```

## Configuration Validation

### Frontend Configuration Validation
The frontend validates environment variables at runtime:

#### Required Variables
- `VITE_BASE_PATH` - Base path for the application (defaults to `/spandan`)
- `VITE_SOCKET_URL` - WebSocket server URL (defaults to window.location.origin)

#### Optional Variables
- `VITE_API_BASE_URL` - API base URL
- `VITE_API_TIMEOUT`, `VITE_API_RETRY_COUNT`, `VITE_API_RETRY_DELAY` - API behavior
- `VITE_THEME`, `VITE_ENABLE_SOUNDS`, `VITE_KEYBOARD_SHORTCUTS` - UI/UX
- `VITE_SAMAGAMA_URL`, `VITE_SAMAGAMA_CLIENT_ID` - SSO integration
- And many more for various features

#### Validation Rules
1. **VITE_BASE_PATH**: Valid URL path format
2. **VITE_SOCKET_URL**: Valid URL
3. **VITE_API_BASE_URL**: Valid URL if provided
4. **VITE_MODE**: Must be valid environment
5. **VITE_THEME**: Must be valid theme option

#### Runtime Validation
```javascript
// frontend/src/config.js
const BASE_PATH = import.meta.env.VITE_BASE_PATH || ''
const API_URL = BASE_PATH + '/api'
const SOCKET_URL = import.meta.env.VITE_SOCKET_URL || window.location.origin
```

## Configuration Management

### Local Development
```bash
# Use .env.local file for local development
# Copy and customize frontend/.env.example to frontend/.env.local

cd frontend
# Edit frontend/.env.local
# Start application
npm run dev
```

### Production Deployment
```bash
# Use environment variables for production
# Set variables via deployment platform

cd frontend
# Install dependencies
npm install

# Build for production
npm run build

# Deploy to hosting platform (Vercel, Netlify, etc.)
```

### Testing Configuration
```bash
# Use local configuration for testing
cd frontend

export VITE_BASE_PATH=/spandan
test locally using .env.local

# Run tests
npm test
```

