- [ ] Run application

### Production Deployment
- [ ] Set secure environment variables
- [ ] Configure reverse proxy (if using)
- [ ] Set up monitoring and logging
- [ ] Test all functionality
- [ ] Deploy to production

### Ongoing Maintenance
