frontend/
# cp .env.example .env.local
# Edit .env.local
# npm run dev

# Set up production
frontend/
# Edit .env.local for production
# npm run build
```

### Essential Variables
```bash
# Required (minimum)
VITE_BASE_PATH=/spandan
VITE_SOCKET_URL=http://localhost:3001

# Optional (configure as needed)
VITE_MODE=development
VITE_API_BASE_URL=/api
VITE_LOG_LEVEL=info
VITE_ENABLE_SSO=true
```

### Configuration Files
```
frontend/
├── .env.example          # Configuration template
